description:
On Thanksgiving Day, 2018, Stephen Andrew Pope was born, lived for one hour and twenty-eight minutes, and died. Though his life was short, he touched the hearts of many people. Witness the extraordinary life of the infant that breathed life into a broken community, gave hope to the hopeless, and lived the truth of the Gospel with every breath. He truly was Born to Reveal the Works of God.

Producers & Directors: Jeremy Pope, Lyndsey Pope
